    "name": "Dinosaurs in Place",
    "steam_appid": 3305650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305650/extras/0131a19b1c21ea93fc501c5f9f7b60fb.avif?t=1741107635\" width=800 height=62 /></span><br>欢迎来到 <strong>Dinosaurs in Place</strong>！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您准备好踏上史前冒险了吗？在 <strong>Dinosaurs in Place</strong> 中，您将结识40个独特的恐龙，每个都有自己的形状和个性。您的任务是将它们放置在网格上，使其完美适应指定的空间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战100个引人入胜的关卡，每个关卡都会对您的逻辑和想象力提出挑战。移动并旋转恐龙模型，找到完美的组合。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>40种独特的恐龙</strong><br>收集40种手绘的恐龙，形状和尺寸各异，每一种都带来独特的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100个精心设计的关卡</strong><br>探索100个关卡，保持你的思维敏捷，提供数小时引人入胜的游戏体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单直观的控制</strong><br>轻松使用鼠标左右键进行操作——适合所有技能水平的玩家。只需用鼠标左键抓取一个图形并移动到所需位置，然后用鼠标右键旋转以达到完美契合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>富有氛围的音乐伴奏</strong><br>享受放松的音乐和声音，将你带入迷人的恐龙世界。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>便捷的提示系统</strong><br>在某个关卡卡住了吗？别担心！游戏提供了一个提示系统，会高亮显示图形的可能放置位置，帮助你轻松前进。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305650/extras/cc6d7981f5b2d4eb6698f9435f50b2b3.poster.avif?t=1741107635\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305650/extras/cc6d7981f5b2d4eb6698f9435f50b2b3.webm?t=1741107635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305650/extras/cc6d7981f5b2d4eb6698f9435f50b2b3.mp4?t=1741107635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dinosaurs in Place</strong> 是引人入胜的谜题和惊艳的图形的完美结合，带给你数小时的愉快娱乐。加入我们的史前世界，展示你的逻辑技能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305650/extras/0ae38130e7e2e32f3801975e083705f3.webp?t=1741107635\" width=800 height=50 /></span></p>",
